In [308]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt #     

tmp_df = df.drop_duplicates(["title", "publishedAt"]).sort_values("publishedAt")
gen_df = pd.DataFrame(tmp_df[["title", "publishedAt"]])

videos = gen_df.groupby("publishedAt").count()["title"]

plt.figure(figsize=(9, 5))

plt.plot(videos.index, videos.values)

plt.title("     ")
plt.xlabel(" ")
plt.ylabel("-  ")

plt.xticks(rotation=45, fontsize = 8)

plt.grid(True)

plt.show()

tmp_df = df.groupby("country").count()["title"]

plt.figure(figsize=(9, 5))

plt.title("    ")
plt.xlabel("")
plt.ylabel("-  ")

plt.bar(tmp_df.index, tmp_df.values)

plt.grid(True, axis='y')

plt.show()
